trans-unit.source: Represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<CipherData>" name="<CipherData>" href=""></xref> element in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Representerer den <xref uid="langword_csharp_<CipherData>" name="<CipherData>" href=""> </xref> element i XML-kryptering.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan arves.

trans-unit.source: The CipherData class represents the `<CipherData>` element in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: CipherData klassen representerer den `<CipherData>` element i XML-kryptering.

trans-unit.source: It is a required element that provides the encrypted data.
trans-unit.target: Det er et nødvendig element som inneholder de krypterte dataene.

trans-unit.source: It must either contain the encrypted data as base64-encoded text of the `<CipherValue>` element, or provide a reference to an external location containing the encrypted data using the `<CipherReference>` element.
trans-unit.target: Det må inneholde de krypterte dataene som base64-kodede tekst for den `<CipherValue>` element, eller bruk en referanse til en ekstern plassering som inneholder krypterte data ved hjelp av den `<CipherReference>` elementet.

trans-unit.source: In many cases, you do not need to directly create a new instance of the CipherData class.
trans-unit.target: Du trenger ikke å opprette en ny forekomst av klassen CipherData direkte i mange tilfeller.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.EncryptedXml%2A>, <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>, and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> classes create instances for you.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.EncryptedXml%2A>, <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>, og <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey>klasser opprette forekomster.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.EncryptedXml%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > A CipherData object can have either a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherReference> property or a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherValue%2A> property, but not both.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > CipherData for et objekt kan ha enten en <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherReference>egenskapen eller <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherValue%2A>egenskapen, men ikke begge deler.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherValue%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherReference>
